Add an explicit database entry to a fleet spec

Usage: sleet db add [OPTIONS] --spec <SPEC> <URL>

Arguments:
  <URL>
          Object-store URL of the database root

Options:
      --spec <SPEC>
          Path to the fleet spec TOML file

      --services <SERVICES>
          Services for the entry (default: inherit `[defaults]`)

      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format

          Possible values:
          - text: Human-readable text
          - json: JSON matching the subcommand's response schema
          
          [default: text]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
